txt.en: 'We must free any Nurnhoth we find held captive in Orodir. They deserve to experience the freedom I have known. Though only for a brief time, the freedom I held brought beauty to my life in this dark land.'
Orodir is located next to Naerband.\n\nYou should free Nurnhoth.
Orodir is located next to Naerband.\n\nYou should find keys at Orodir.
The prison fortress of Naerband has been rounding up anyone and everyone in an effort to enforce a twisted law over the lands.
